AYCHtdtfO37F55_-Pwl_bvkZ1Mt03WYqzRe7yqsV5IPQAA&oe=677E6CC5"}, {"file_name": "screenshot3-GoalieMode.png", "id": "324634503308151", "uri": "https://scontent-sin11-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982563_324634506641484_1756516055424560387_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=XHTrCh4TxbYQ7kNvgGiqbxK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin11-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBWc60ynz5PIPjwpl6c1Ftirkt89BCfJNwNyO--DmN0YQ&oe=677E4FCD"}, {"file_name": "screenshot2-defenderMode.png", "id": "690323585937024", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57575356_690323589270357_6573697315152692856_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=W0RNiPEYTUkQ7kNvgG8xDis&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAxNuVr6JQpQJhcttwlOS0AmvZJCG9MUCucVJJ1tzWR_Q&oe=677E5F55"}, {"file_name": "MGPost2560x1440Content.png", "id": "331756112747064", "uri": "https://scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982600_331756119413730_2102063463568969114_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ECCpK5MZFBsQ7kNvgFL2BrA&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA3J5xmwEdJsiUrOs9aG9KHzeR1bO4DhNe86iTKs0m3UQ&oe=677E5B26"}, {"file_name": "screenshot1-mainmenu.png", "id": "1492025668264421", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031430_1492025671597754_8047331025133290047_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=x1k-CbeecQgQ7kNvgF_EOJV&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAoBoGCsfEkuCGgudAg2t3so2HHKvZd6ZTmuvg1qS7_gQ&oe=677E8033"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "2560X1440.png", "id": "696966651969139", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982522_696966655302472_5287169594548358940_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hULfdPIed_IQ7kNvgGiBz4-&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCqybidiyyzhCnf_996fNkAv8zEMtgg4bU9uVgrqvgCmQ&oe=677E67C3"}, "display_name": "LAXVR Skills", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**LAXVR Skills: Immersive Lacrosse in Virtual Reality**\n\nDive deep into the thrilling world of lacrosse like never before with LAXVR Skills, an unparalleled virtual reality experience. Crafted for both enthusiasts and novices, this game offers a chance to immerse yourself fully in the realm of lacrosse from a first-person perspective. Here's a glimpse into what awaits you:\n\n1. **Four Main Game Modes:** \n   **Shooting Mode:** Hone your shooting skills, master different techniques, and aim for that perfect shot.\n   **Goalie Mode:** Stand tall between the posts, anticipate your opponent's moves, and make that crucial save.\n   **Defender Mode:** Learn the art of defense, stop the attackers in their tracks, and reclaim the ball.\n   **The Medicine Game:** Embark on a historical journey that pays homage to the deep-rooted origins and traditions of lacrosse. Experience the soul of the game and its spiritual significance.\n\n2. **Casual Play Modes:** \n   **Wall Ball:** Perfect for those who cherish the simple joys of the game. Bounce, catch, and repeat. Sharpen your hand-eye coordination and reflexes.\n   **Free Shoot:** Sometimes, all you need is the open field, a stick, a goal, and a ball. Practice your shots or just enjoy the serenity of the virtual field.\n\n3. **Community and Competition:** \n   **Leaderboards:** Push your limits! Challenge yourself, compete with your friends, and see how you rank globally in the LAX VR community. ", "short_description": "Dive into LAXVR Skills and elevate your lacrosse game! Engage in thrilling drills: fire precision shots, stuff attackers, and de-twig attackers with decisive checks. Can you score a 2-pointer past our goalie? Stop a 12-yard step down shot? Or shut down an attacker's split dodge? Challenge awaits in every corner!"}]}, "developer_name": "Duper Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://laxvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Duper Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "ht